<h2>Dynamic Design Gallery</h2>
<p>Vistora's online gallery at <a href="https://vistoraclosets.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">vistoraclosets.com</a> features select closet designs with interactive feature buttons that reveal specific product information for each item in the design — helping dealers and homeowners plan their perfect closet with confidence.</p>

<h2>Why Add Closets to Your Dealership?</h2>
<p>Many kitchen customers also need walk-in closet systems, reach-in closet organization, pantry storage, and mudroom solutions. Vistora's pre-assembled modular approach means dealers don't need specialized closet installation expertise — the simplified component system is far easier to design and install than traditional closet brands. It's an opportunity to capture whole-home projects, increase average order value, and keep business that would otherwise go to a dedicated closet company.</p>

